Currency Task

 solution has two sub-projects and they are as the following 
-	WPFClient serve as client side (WPF) 
-	WCFService serve as server side 

WPFClient  project features
-	Using MVVM design pattern for structured and minitablet code 
-	Using Adorners for custom styling 
-	Button animations 
-	Input validation 
-	Error handling 
WCFService project features 
-	Split number based on type (Million, Thousand, Hundred, Tens, Units) 
-	Math features exist in C#
-	Validation 
-	Error handling 
Note: Before running the project, run WCFService first and check if accessible from browser, 
then copy the URL and paste in WPFClient App.Config file
